---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout pageKey="3kw-solar-system.html" headerVariant="guide">

<!-- HERO -->

<section class="py-20">

<div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">

<div class="inline-block bg-indigo-100 text-indigo-700 px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">
Residential Solar Guide
</div>

<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold mt-6">
3kW Solar System Price,
Subsidy & Savings Guide
</h1>

<p class="text-slate-600 text-lg mt-6 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
A 3kW rooftop solar system is one of the most popular choices for Indian homes.
It is typically suitable for households with monthly electricity bills between ₹3,000 and ₹5,000.
</p>

</div>

</section>

<!-- QUICK FACTS -->

<section class="pb-12">

<div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">

<div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-5">

<div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-3xl shadow-sm border">
<div class="text-sm text-slate-500">Monthly Bill</div>
<div class="text-2xl font-bold mt-2">
₹3,000–₹5,000
</div>
</div>

<div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-3xl shadow-sm border">
<div class="text-sm text-slate-500">Roof Area</div>
<div class="text-2xl font-bold mt-2">
240–300 sq ft
</div>
</div>

<div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-3xl shadow-sm border">
<div class="text-sm text-slate-500">Panels</div>
<div class="text-2xl font-bold mt-2">
6–8
</div>
</div>

<div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-3xl shadow-sm border">
<div class="text-sm text-slate-500">Best For</div>
<div class="text-2xl font-bold mt-2">
Families
</div>
</div>

</div>

</div>

</section>

<!-- COST SECTION -->

<section class="py-12">

<div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">

<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-sm border">

<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">
Estimated 3kW Solar System Cost
</h2>

<div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">

<div class="bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-2xl">
<div class="text-slate-500 text-sm">
Typical Cost
</div>

<div class="text-3xl font-bold mt-2">
₹1.6L–₹2.2L
</div>
</div>

<div class="bg-emerald-50 p-6 rounded-2xl">
<div class="text-emerald-700 text-sm">
Government Subsidy*
</div>

<div class="text-3xl font-bold mt-2 text-emerald-700">
Available
</div>
</div>

<div class="bg-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-2xl">
<div class="text-indigo-700 text-sm">
Typical Payback
</div>

<div class="text-3xl font-bold mt-2 text-indigo-700">
4–6 Years
</div>
</div>

</div>

<p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-6">
*Actual pricing and subsidy eligibility vary by location, installer, equipment selection and prevailing government policies.
</p>

</div>

</div>

</section>

<!-- WHO SHOULD BUY -->

<section class="py-12">

<div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">

<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">
Who Should Consider A 3kW Solar System?
</h2>

<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl border shadow-sm">

<ul class="space-y-4 text-slate-700">

<li>✓ Homes with monthly bills between ₹3,000 and ₹5,000</li>

<li>✓ Small to medium-sized families</li>

<li>✓ Independent houses with available rooftop space</li>

<li>✓ Homeowners looking to reduce electricity costs long term</li>

<li>✓ Households interested in government subsidy programs</li>

</ul>

</div>

</div>

</section>

<!-- BENEFITS -->

<section class="py-12">

<div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">

<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">
Benefits Of A 3kW Solar System
</h2>

<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">

<div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-3xl border">
<h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-3">
Lower Electricity Bills
</h3>
<p class="text-slate-600">
Generate your own electricity and reduce dependence on the grid.
</p>
</div>

<div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-3xl border">
<h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-3">
Government Incentives
</h3>
<p class="text-slate-600">
Eligible households may benefit from available rooftop solar subsidy schemes.
</p>
</div>

<div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-3xl border">
<h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-3">
Long-Term Savings
</h3>
<p class="text-slate-600">
Solar systems typically operate for 25 years or more.
</p>
</div>

<div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-3xl border">
<h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-3">
Energy Independence
</h3>
<p class="text-slate-600">
Protect yourself against future electricity tariff increases.
</p>
</div>

</div>

</div>

</section>

<!-- FAQ -->

<section class="py-12">

<div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">

<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">
Frequently Asked Questions
</h2>

<div class="space-y-6">

<div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl border">
<h3 class="font-semibold">
How much electricity can a 3kW solar system generate?
</h3>
<p class="mt-2 text-slate-600">
Generation depends on location, weather and installation quality. Actual output varies.
</p>
</div>

<div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl border">
<h3 class="font-semibold">
How much roof space is required?
</h3>
<p class="mt-2 text-slate-600">
Most installations require approximately 240–300 square feet of shadow-free roof area.
</p>
</div>

<div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl border">
<h3 class="font-semibold">
Can batteries be added later?
</h3>
<p class="mt-2 text-slate-600">
Many systems can be upgraded later with battery storage, subject to technical compatibility.
</p>
</div>

<div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl border">
<h3 class="font-semibold">
Is subsidy guaranteed?
</h3>
<p class="mt-2 text-slate-600">
No. Subsidies are subject to government policies, eligibility criteria and approval processes.
</p>
</div>

</div>

</div>

</section>

<!-- CTA -->

<section class="py-20">

<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">

<div class="bg-slate-900 text-white rounded-[2rem] p-10">

<h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">
See If A 3kW System Is Right For You
</h2>

<p class="text-slate-300 mb-8">
Get a personalized solar recommendation based on your electricity bill and location.
</p>

<a href="index.html"
class="inline-block bg-emerald-600 hover:bg-emerald-700 px-8 py-4 rounded-2xl font-bold transition">
Calculate My Solar Savings
</a>

</div>

</div>

</section>

<!-- FOOTER -->

</BaseLayout>
